bd系统将从发动机的运行状况随时监控汽车是否尾气超标，一旦超标会马上发出警示。 车辆obd检测是什么汽车obd检测是什么意思车上obd是车载自动诊断系统，其作用是：对于出现故障的部位、部件进行故障定位和描述，便于维修；对于导致排放超标的故障进行报警，以提示污染物排放对环境影响增加。"},"attached_info":"CkAI+7rXwe3NxuZMEAMaCTExMjEzMDI0NiDDg7e6BjAAOEtABXIKNTc2ODIxNjg1N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-686fb6a5c6f0cd11083af7268022b888_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1733397489.993686","card_id":"Q_5812889831","target":{"id":5812889831,"title":"工作中怀疑最大领导不喜欢你，怎么办？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/5812889831","type":"question","created":1733194764,"answer_count":113,"follower_count":155,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2566,16475,27919,159476,2988052],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"时不时需要和大领导对接下，但是感觉他的态度不是很好，当然是对比他对其他同级（于我）同事的态度。"},"attached_info":"CkEI+7rXwe3NxuZMEAMaCTExMjEzOTE3NCCM6Lm6BjAAOJsBQAZyCjU4MTI4ODk4MzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d72f61f428bd6606ef6ee901daceaedc_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1733397489.994034","card_id":"Q_5814521413","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":5814521413,"title":"《白夜破晓》导演刘英剑称「第二部更关注的是人性，而不是推理案件的难度」，对于这个观点你怎么看？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/5814521413","type":"question","created":1733195903,"answer_count":91,"follower_count":105,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2102